\id EZR
\h Ɛizra
\toc1 Ɛizra
\toc2 Ɛizra
\toc3 Ɛiz.
\mt1 Ɛizra
\c 1
\s1 Řumur n Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas amezwaru n ujeǧid Kurac n Lfurs, ḥima ad ittwakemmeř wawař n SIDI zeg uqemmum n Irmiya, issekkar SIDI buḥbeř n Kurac ajeǧid n Lfurs maḥend ad ittwabarreḥ di marra tageldit nnes s uqemmum d tira: \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt [2 Im. 36:22, 23; Irm. 25:12; 29:10; Dan. 9:2]\x*
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n ijenwan, iwca ayi marra tigeldiwin n temmurt uca netta igga xafi, ad as bniɣ ict n Taddart di Urcalim, tenni \add iǧan\add* di Yahuda.
\v 3 Man wen zzaywem zi řgens nnes, ad yiři AREBBI akides, ejj i-t ad igeɛɛed ɣar Urcalim, tenni \add iǧan\add* di Yahuda, ad ibna Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil. Aqa-t d AREBBI wenni \add izeddɣen\add* di Urcalim.
\v 4 Qaɛ wenni iqqimen ɛad di \add ca n wemcan\add* n marra imucan mani izeddeɣ d abarrani, ad kkaren iryazen n wemcan nnes ad as wcen afus s nnuqart d wureɣ, s wagřa d řmař, \add u man aya\add* sennej i tewhibt immewcen s řxaḍar i Taddart n AREBB di Urcalim.’”
\b
\m 
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* kkaren izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* n Yahuda d Binyamin uřa d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen u marra inni umi issfaq AREBBI buḥbeř, maḥend ad geɛɛden ḥima ad bnan Taddart n SIDI wenni \add izeddɣen\add* di Urcalim.
\v 6 Marra inni d asen dd-innḍen wcin asen afus s řeqcuɛ n nnuqart, s wureɣ, s wagřa, s řmař u s řeqcuɛ iɣřan, břa min immewcen s řxaḍar.
\v 7 Ajeǧid Kurac issuffeɣ řeqcuɛ n Taddart n SIDI, tinni tuɣa iksi Nabuxadnaṣṣar zi Urcalim uca igga i-tent di taddart n arebbi nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt 2 Ij. 24:13; 2 Im. 36:7\x*
\v 8 Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs, issuffeɣ i-tent ɣar barra s ufus n Mitradat, bab n txubay, wenni tent iwcin s řeḥsab i Cicbaṣṣar, řḥakem n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Ɛiz. 5:14\x*
\m 
\v 9 Wa tuɣa d řqedd nsen: třatin n ṭṭbaṣa n wureɣ, ařef n ṭṭbaṣa n nnuqart, tesɛa u-ɛicrin n řemwas,
\v 10 třatin n ifenjařen n wureɣ, arebɛa-mya u-ɛecra n ifenjařen inneɣni n nnuqart d wařef n řeqcuɛ nneɣnit.
\v 11 Marra řeqcuɛ n wureɣ d nnuqart tuɣa iwḍen xemsa-ařaf u-arebɛa-mya. Marra aya yiwyi t Cicbaṣṣar akides, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ayt n lmenfa inni ittwanedhen zi Babil ɣar Urcalim.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Lista n ayt n tmeḥbast nni iɛeqben ak-d Zarubbabil
\m 
\v 1 Ina d ayt n lɛamala nni dd-igeɛɛden zi tmeḥbast - imenfiyyen nni dd-iwyi Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, di lmenfa ɣar Babil - uca ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim d Yahuda, kuř ijj ɣar tendint nnes,
\v 2 \add uca\add* usin-dd ak-d Zarubbabil, Yahucaɛ, Nahamya, Saraya, Raɛlaya, Murdaxai, Bilcan, Misfar, Biɣway, Raḥum d Baɛna. Wa d \bd řqedd n yeryazen n řgens n Israil\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 2:2 \fk řqedd\ft - niɣ ‘lɛadad’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 3 Ayt n n Farɛuc, ařfayen u-mya u-tnayen u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 4 Ayt n Cafaṭya, teřt-mya u-tnayen u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 5 Ayt n Araḥ, sebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 6 Iḥenjiren n Fahat-Mu’ab, zeg iḥenjiren n Yecuɛa \add d\add* Yu’ab, ařfayen u temnem-mya u-tenɛac \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 7 Ayt n Ɛilam, ařef u-mitayn u-arebɛa u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 8 Ayt n Zattu, tesɛa-mya u-xemsa u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 9 Ayt n Zakkay, sebɛa-mya u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 10 Ayt n Bani, setta-mya u-tnayen u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 11 Ayt n Babay, setta-mya u-třata u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 12 Ayt n Ɛarjad, ařef u-mitayn u-tnayen u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 13 Ayt n Aduniqam, setta-mya u-setta u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*.\x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Ij. 10:14; 2 Im. 9:13; Asa. 17:9. \x*
\m 
\v 14 Ayt n Biɣway, ařfayen u-setta u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 15 Ayt n Ɛadin, arebɛa-mya u-arebɛa u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 16 Ayt n Aṭir, zi Ḥizqiya, tmenya u-tesɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 17 Ayt n Biṣay, teřt-mya u-třata u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 18 Ayt n Yura, mya u-tenɛac \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 19 Ayt n Ḥacum, mitayen u-třata u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 20 Ayt n Jibbar, xemsa u-tesɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 21 Ayt n Bayt-Laḥm, mya u-třata u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 22 Iryazen ni Naṭufa, setta u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 23 Iryazen n Ɛanatut, mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 24 Arrawen n Ɛazmawet, tnayen u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 25 Ayt n Qaryat-Ɛarim, Kafira d Biɛrut, sebɛa-mya u-třata u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 26 Ayt n Rama d Jabaɛ, setta-mya u-waḥed u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 27 Iryazen n Mixmas, mya u-tnayen u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 28 Iryazen n Bayt-Il d Ɛay, mitayen u-třata u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 29 Ayt n Nabu, tnayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 30 Ayt n Maɣbic, mya u-setta u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 31 Ayt n \add ijj n\add* Ɛilam nneɣni, ařef u-mitayn u-arebɛa u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 32 Ayt n Ḥarim, teřt-mya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 33 Ayt n Lud, Ḥadid d Unu, sebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 34 Ayt n Ariḥa, teřt-mya u-xemsa u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 35 Ayt n Sana’a, teřt-ařaf u-setta-mya u-třatin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 36 \bd Ikehhanen.\bd*
\m Ayt n Yadaɛya, zi taddart n Yecuɛa, tesɛa-mya u-třata u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 37 Ayt n Immir, ařef u-tnayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 38 Ayt n Facḥur, ařef u-mitayn u-sebɛa u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 39 Ayt n Ḥarim, ařef u-sbeɛṭac \add n yeryazen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 40 \bd Ilawiyyen.\bd*
\m Ayt n Yecuɛa, ayt n Qadmiyil, zeg ayt n Hudawya, arebɛa u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 41 \bd Imedyazen.\bd*
\m Ayt n Asaf, mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.\f ◼ \fr 2:41 \fk Imedyazen\ft - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 42 \bd Ayt n iɛessasen n tewwura.\bd*
\m Ayt n Callum, ayt n Aṭir, ayt n Ṭalmun, ayt n Ɛaqqub, ayt n Ḥaṭiṭa, ayt n Cubay, aqa aten \add jmiɛ\add* mya u-tesɛa u-třatin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 43 \bd Imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant.\bd*
\m Ayt n Ṣiḥa, ayt n Ḥasufa, ayt n Ṭabaɛut,
\m 
\v 44 ayt n Qiruc, ayt n Siɛaha, ayt n Fadun,
\m 
\v 45 ayt n Labana, ayt n Ḥajaba, ayt n Ɛaqqub,
\m 
\v 46 ayt n Ḥajab, ayt n Camlay, ayt n Ḥanan,
\m 
\v 47 ayt n Jadil, ayt n Ḥajar, ayt n Ra’aya,
\m 
\v 48 ayt n Raṣin, ayt n Naqquda, ayt n Jazzam,
\m 
\v 49 ayt n Ɛuzza, ayt n Fasiḥ, ayt n Bisay,
\m 
\v 50 ayt n Asna, ayt n Maɛunim, ayt n Nafusim,
\m 
\v 51 ayt n Baqbuq, ayt n Ḥaqufa, ayt n Ḥarḥur,
\m 
\v 52 ayt n Baṣlut, ayt n Maḥida, ayt n Ḥarca,
\m 
\v 53 ayt n Barqus, ayt n Sisara, ayt n Tamaḥ,
\m 
\v 54 ayt n Nasiḥ, ayt n Ḥaṭifa.
\b
\m 
\v 55 \bd Ayt n imsexxaren n Suliman.\bd*
\m Ayt n Suṭay, ayt n Sufarat, ayt n Faruda,
\m 
\v 56 ayt n Yaɛala, ayt n Darqun, ayt n Jiddil,
\m 
\v 57 ayt n Cafaṭya, ayt n Ḥaṭṭil, ayt n Fuxarat-ha-Ḍabayim d ayt n Ami.
\b
\m 
\v 58 Marra imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant d iḥenjiren n imsexxaren n Suliman, aqa aten \add jmiɛ\add* teřt-mya u-tnayen u-tesɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 59 Ina d inni dd-igeɛɛden zi Tal-Milaḥ, Tal-Ḥarca, Karub, Addan d Immir, \add maca\add* war zemmaren ad ssecnen zi jjihet n taddart n řejdud nsen niɣ zi jjihet n zzariɛet nsen, aqa nitni \add qarsen-dd\add* zi Israil:
\m 
\v 60 ayt n Dalaja, ayt n Ṭubiyya, ayt n Naquda, setta-mya u-tnayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 61 Uca zeg ayt n ikehhanen: ayt n Ḥabaya, ayt n Haqquṣ, ayt n Barzillay, \add aqa zzaysen inni\add* iwyen ict n temɣart zi yessis n Ujilɛadi Barzillay u ttwařaɣan s yisem nnes.
\m 
\v 62 Nitni arzun x tewriqt n uzemmem nsen \add deg wedlis n taṣiřet\add*, maca war tt ufin. S uyenni ttwassuffɣen nitni zi tukehhant.
\v 63 Lwali ameqqran inna asen, war ttᵉtten zi tmesřayin iqeddsen qaɛ ař ɣa ikkar ijj n ukehhan ak-d Urim d Tummim.
\b
\m 
\v 64 Marra agraw \add n řgens\add* \add tuɣa di\add* tnayen u-rebɛin-ařef u-teřt-mya u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*,
\v 65 nhřa isemɣan d tiyya nsen. Ina tuɣa aten marra sebɛa-ařaf u-teřt-mya u-sebɛa u-třatin uca ɣarsen mitayen n imedyazen d tmedyazin. \f ◼ \fr 2:65 \fk imedyazen d tmedyazin\ft - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen d tmeɣnujin’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 66 Iysan nsen \add tuɣa aten di\add* sebɛa-mya u-setta u-třatin, u isardan nsen \add tuɣa aten di\add* mitayen u-xemsa u-rebɛin.
\m 
\v 67 Iřeɣman nsen \add tuɣa aten di\add* arebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-třatin \add u\add* iɣyař nsen \add tuɣa aten di\add* sebɛa-mya u-ɛicrin.
\b
\m 
\v 68 Umi dd-yusin ɣar Taddart n SIDI di Urcalim, wcin ca n izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* s řxaḍar i Taddart n AREBBI ḥima ad tt ssbedden deg wemcan nnes.
\v 69 Nitni wcin i ssenduq n txubay i řxedmet anect n wagřa nsen waḥit u-settin-ařef n draxmat n wureɣ d xemsa-ařaf n minayat n nnuqart d mya n tcamirat i ikehhanen. \f ◼ \fr 2:69 \fk tixubay\ft - niɣ ‘řeknuz’.\f*
\m 
\v 70 Ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d ca zi řgens d imedyazen d iɛessasen n tewwart d imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant ggin ad zedɣen di tneddam nsen u uřa d marra Israil \add igga ad izdeɣ\add* di tneddam nnes.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Beddu n řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* dd-yiweḍ uyur wiss sebɛa u ayt n Israil tuɣa aten di tneddam, issmun řgens am yijj n weryaz di Urcalim.
\v 2 Ikkar Yahucaɛ, mmis n Yuṣadaq, ak-d aytmas, ikehhanen, d Zarubbabil, mmis n Caɛaltiyil, ak-d aytmas, uca bnan aɛalṭar n AREBBI n Israil, ḥima ad xas qeddmen tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ am mammec tura di Ccariɛa n Musa, aryaz n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Aɛwd. 12:5, 6\x*
\v 3 Nitni ssbedden aɛalṭar x dsusa nnes \add mani t tuɣa d amezwaru\add*, waxxa tewḍa-dd xasen tiggʷudi zi řegnus n temmura, uca qeddmen xas tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i SIDI, tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i tuffut u i tmeddit. \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Řxř. 28:3\x*
\v 4 Nitni ɛeyyden \add ɛawed\add* Řɛid n Iɛuccuten, am mammec t yura, uca \add qeddmen\add* tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ, ass iḍfar umas. \add Tuɣa\add* řqedd \add nsent\add* i yijj n wass \add ɛlaḥsab min ittwaggen\add* i wass nni. \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Lawi 23:34; Řxř. 29:12\x*
\v 5 Awarni as \add qeddmen nitni\add* taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ n řebda, \add tiɣarṣa\add* i wussan n uyur n jdid u i marra řeɛyudat ittwaggen n SIDI inni tuɣa ittwaqeddsen, u \add ɛawed tiɣarṣa n\add* kuř ijj wenni iṭṭewɛen ḥima ad iqeddem ict n tewhibt s řxaḍar i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Řxř. 28:11-15; Naḥ. 10:34\x*
\m 
\v 6 Zeg wass amezwaru n uyur wiss sebɛa bdan nitni ad qeddmen tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i SIDI, maca dsas n Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI war ittwagg \add ɛad\add*.
\v 7 Wcin nnuqart i imaṣṣuten u i yinni ineqqcen akeccuḍ, uca i \add ayt n\add* Sidun u i \add ayt n\add* Ṣur \add wcin nitni\add* macca d tissit d zzect, maḥend ad awyen akeccuḍ n tneglin n Lubnan ɣar řebḥar ɣar Yafa ɛlaḥsab ttesriḥ i d asen iwca Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs.
\v 8 Deg useggʷas wiss tnayen awarni wawaḍ nsen ɣar Taddart n AREBBI di Urcalim, deg uyur wiss tnayen, bdan Zarubbabil, mmis n Caɛaltiyil, d Yahucaɛ, mmis n Yuṣadaq, d aytmas nsen i iqqimen, ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d marra inni dd-yusin zi tmeḥbast ɣar Urcalim, \add di řxedmet\add*. Nitni ggin Ilawiyyen zi ɛicřin iseggʷusa sennej maḥend ad ṭṭfen acbar x řxedmet n Taddart n SIDI.
\v 9 Uca ikkar Yecuɛa d iḥenjiren nnes d aytmas, ak-d Qadmyil d iḥenjiren nnes, ayt n Yahuda, am yijj n weryaz maḥend ad ṭṭfen acbar x yinni iggin řxedmet di Taddart n AREBBI, \add u ɛawed\add* iḥenjiren n Ḥinadad ak-d iḥenjiren nsen d aytmatsen Ilawiyyen.
\m 
\v 10 \add Umi\add* tuɣa ibennayen ssrusan dsas i Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, ssbedden nitni ikehhanen s warruḍ nsen ak-d řebwaq, uřa d Ilawiyyen, ayt n Asaf, s teǧunin n wuzzař, ḥima ad ssemɣaren SIDI am mammec tuɣa i d asen isscen ufus n Dawud, ajeǧid n Israil.
\v 11 Nitni ɣennjen s nnubtat i SIDI s usemɣar d uqadi, aqa Netta iṣbeḥ minzi tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren x Israil tᵉttɣima i řebda. U marra řgens isɣuy s yijj n usřiwřew imɣar i usemɣar n SIDI maɣar dsas i Taddart n SIDI tuɣa immars. \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Izhd. 136:1 \x*
\v 12 Aṭṭas n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add*, iwessura inni iẓrin Taddart tamezwarut, run s tmijja ijehden umi ittwagg dsas n Taddart-a zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, \add maca uřa d\add* aṭṭas arenyen di tmijja \add nsen\add* s usřiwřew u s řefraḥet,
\v 13 ařami war izemmar řgens ad meyyzen jar řḥess n usřiwřew d řḥess n iɣuyyan s imeṭṭawen n řgens, minzi řgens isɣuy s yijj n usřiwřew imɣar ařami ittwaseř řḥess zi řaggʷaj.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Řeɛkaset x řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* sřen iɣrimen n Yahuda d Binyamin, aqa ayt n lmenfa tuɣa bennan Zzawect Tameqqrant i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil,
\v 2 usin-dd nitni ɣar Zarubbabil d izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* uca nnan asen: “Ejj aneɣ ad nebna \add jmiɛ\add* akidwem, minzi uřa d neccin narezzu AREBBI, am kenniw, maɣar neccin tuɣa nqeddem tiɣarṣi zeg wussan n Asarḥaddun, ajeǧid n Accur, wenni d aneɣ da issgeɛɛden.” \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt 2 Ij. 17:29-41 \x*
\v 3 Maca Zarubbabil d Yahucaɛ d izeǧifen iqqimen jar ibabaten n Israil, nnan asen: “War \add iǧi\add* i kenniw d neccin maḥend ad nebna \add jmiɛ\add* ict n Taddart i AREBBI nneɣ. Neccin weḥḥdneɣ ad tt nebna i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, am mammec i d aneɣ yumur ujeǧid Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs.” \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt Ɛiz. 1:1, 2, 3\x*
\m 
\v 4 Uca imsar, aqa řgens n temmurt ssarxun ifassen n řgens n Yahuda uca ssiggʷiden ten x řebni.
\v 5 Cran imcawaren ḍidd nsen, maḥend ad ssbeṭṭřen anway nsen, u \add aya ikka\add* marra ussan n Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs, ař tagelda n Dariyus, ajeǧid n Lfurs.
\v 6 Umi tuɣa Aḥacwiruc d ajeǧid, ɣar beddu n tgelda nnes, uran nitni ijj n ucetci ḍidd i imezdaɣ n Yahuda d Urcalim.
\m 
\v 7 Deg wussan n Artaḥcasta yura Biclam \add ak-d\add* Mitradat \add d\add* Ṭabayil d iɛciren nnes inneɣni, i ujeǧid Artaḥcasta, ajeǧid n Lfurs. Tuɣa tabrat tura s tira n \add iřes n\add* Tramit u tuɣa tarjmen tt \add ɛawed\add* ɣar Tramit.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Raḥum, amsuffeɣ n řeḥkamat, d umarir Cimcay urin ict n tebrat i ujeǧid Artaḥcasta ḍidd i Urcalim, tenni \add dayes yura\add* ammu:
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Raḥum, amsuffeɣ n řeḥkamat, d umarir Cimcay d inni iqqimen zeg iqrinen nsen di řxedmet, řquḍat, imxazniyyen, ayt n ccenɛet d ayt n Lfurs d ayt n Irix d Babilun d Cucan, aqa aten d Iɛilamiyyen,
\v 10 d ccuɛub nneɣni, inni iwyi ten Asnaffar ameqqran amcenneɛ ɣar lmenfa u issezdeɣ i-ten di tendint n Samarya u di jjihet iqqimen x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* ... uca ɛad.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 Ta d tiřemt n tebrat i dd-ssekken nitni i ujeǧid Artaḥcasta:
\b
\m “Imsexxaren nnec, iryazen nni \add iǧan\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* ... uca ɛad.”
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Iři ad issen ujeǧid aqa Udayen i dd-igeɛɛden zi ɣarek, aqa iwḍen-dd ɣarneɣ ɣar Urcalim uca nitni aqa bennan tandint nni iɣewwɣen taɛeffant, aqa ttkemmařen řeḥyuḍ u ɛeddřen dsusa.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ittxeṣṣa ad issen ujeǧid, mařa tandint nni ad tᵉttwassbedd twařa nneɣni u řeḥyuḍ ad ttwakemmřen, aqa nettat war tᵉttic ljizya řa d řeɛcur uřa d ḍḍariba n webrid uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa issexsar arbeḥ n ijeǧiden.
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, umi neccin nettmeǧaḥ macca nneɣ s tmeǧaḥt n řeqṣar u war d aneɣ dd-tusi mařa neccin nxezzar umi ittwassbehdeř ujeǧid, x uyenni nessekk-dd tabrat-a uca nessargeb aya i ujeǧid,
\v 15 ḥima ad arzun deg wedlis n imezruyen n řejdud nwem uca ad tafed deg wedlis n imezruyen uca ad \add zzayes\add* tessned aqa tandint-a d ict n tendint iɣewwɣen, tiwi-dd arrẓiyyet i ijeǧiden u i lɛamalat u zeg wecḥař uya ssekkaran dayes aɣewweɣ. S uyenni tᵉttwahdem tendint-a.
\v 16 Neccin nessargeb ajeǧid, aqa, mařa ad tᵉttwabna tendint-a \add ɛawed\add* uca ad ttwakemmřen řeḥyuḍ nnes, xenni war ɣarek ttᵉttiři ca teṣɣart \add ɛad\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*.”
\b
\m 
\v 17 Issekk ujeǧid tamwarrit i Raḥum, amsuffeɣ n řeḥkamat, u i umarir Cimcay d inni iqqimen zeg iqrinen nsen di řxedmet inni izeddɣen di Samarya, u uřa i yinni iqqimen \add zeddɣen\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*:
\b
\m “Řehna! ... uca ɛad.”
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Tabrat i d aneɣ dd-tessekkem, aqa tᵉttwaɣar xafi nican.
\v 19 Uca \add awarni řami\add* umureɣ \add aya\add*, tᵉttwagg ict n tarezzut uca ufin aqa tandint-a tɣewweɣ x ijeǧiden zeg wecḥař uya uca ssekkaren dayes \add řebda\add* aɣewweɣ d řeḥweř.
\v 20 Ɛawed tuɣa \add din\add* ijeǧiden imeqqranen x Urcalim, inni tuɣa iḥekkmen di marra \add jjwayeh\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* ařami tᵉttwaxeǧeṣ asen ljizya d řeɛcur d ḍḍariba n webrid.
\v 21 Iwa, řexxu umurem ad ssbeddem iryazen-a. Tandint war tbenni twařa nneɣnit ař ɣa ittwassuffeɣ zzayi řumur \add i uya\add*.
\v 22 Ɣarwem aqa ad tarxum zi tmesřact-a. Mayemmi ɣa temɣar druct \add ɛad\add* i txessart n ijeǧiden?”
\b
\m 
\v 23 Řami tᵉttwaɣar tebrat n ujeǧid Artaḥcasta i Raḥum d Cimcay, amarir, d iqrinen nsen di řxedmet, uyuren ina s tazřa ɣar Urcalim, ɣar Wudayen uca ssbedden ten \add zi řxedmet nsen\add* s uɣiř u s řxuncet.
\v 24 Xenni tbedd řxedmet i Taddart n Arebbi wenni izeddɣen di Urcalim uca iqqim ibedd ař aseggʷas wiss tnayen n tgelda n Dariyus, ajeǧid n Lfurs.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant deg wussan n Dariyus
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* nebban inabiyyen, inabiyyen Ḥaggay d Zakariyya, mmis n Ɛidu, i Wudayen nni \add iǧan\add* di Yahuda d Urcalim. \add Nabben\add* ɣarsen s Yisem n Arebbi n Israil nni xasen \add ittwařaɣa\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Ḥag. 1:1; Zak. 1:1\x*
\v 2 Xas uca ikkar Zarubbabil, mmis n Caɛaltiyil, d Yahucaɛ, mmis n Yuṣadaq, uca nitni bdan ad bnan Taddart n Arebbi di Urcalim \add ɛawed\add*, uca inabiyyen n Arebbi, inni akidsen ibedden, \add tuɣa aten din\add* akidsen.
\m 
\v 3 Di řweqt nni yusa-dd Tatnay, lwali n \add weqlim\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, ak-d Catar-Buznay u ɣarsen iqrinen nsen di řxedmet. Nitni nnan asen ammu: “Man wen i kenniw yumuren, maḥend ad tebnam Taddart-a u \add maḥend\add* ad tkemmřem řḥiḍ-a?”
\v 4 Xenni nenna asen ismawen n yeryazen i tuɣa ibennan řebni-ya.
\v 5 \add Maca\add* tiṭṭ n Arebbi nsen tuɣa-tt x imɣaren n Wudayen uca nitni ggin war ten ssbeddan \add zi řxedmet\add* ař ɣa taweḍ tmesřact ɣar Dariyus uca awarni aya ad ṭṭfen tabrat x man aya.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Tiřemt n tebrat nni issekk Tatnay, lwali \add n temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, ak-d Catar-Buznay d iqrinen nnes di řxedmet, iqrinen nni \add iǧan\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, ɣar ujeǧid Dariyus.
\m 
\v 7 Nitni ssekken as-dd ict n tebrat tura dayes ammu:
\b
\m “Ad yiři i ujeǧid Dariyus řehna zi marra iɣezdisen!”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Ittxeṣsa ad issen ujeǧid, aqa neccin nuyur ɣar lɛamala n Yahuda, ɣar Taddart n Arebbi ameqqran. Aqa tᵉttwabenna \add Taddart nni\add* s iẓra imeqqranen i ittxeṣṣan ad ttwannḍen \add ɣar wemcan nsen\add*, u ittwattegg ukeccuḍ di řeḥyuḍ. Tteggen nitni řxedmet-a s cḍaret uca teggur mliḥ jar ifassen nsen.
\v 9 Neccin nesseqsa imɣaren-a u nenna \add asen\add* ammu: ‘Man wen i d awem iwcin řumur maḥend ad tessbeddem taddart-a u ad tkemmřem řḥiḍ-a?’
\v 10 Nesseqsa ten uřa x ismawen nsen ḥima ad ac ten-i-dd-nini, ařami niweḍ ad nzemmem ismawen n yeryazen nni iǧan ɣar uzeǧif nsen.
\v 11 Nitni arrin aneɣ-dd, nnan ammu: ‘Neccin d imsexxaren n Arebbi n ijenwan d temmurt u nebna taddart tenni tᵉttwabna danita aṭṭas n iseggʷusa zeg wami. Ijj n ujeǧid d ameqqran n Israil ibna tt u ikemmeř i-tt.
\v 12 Maca awarni řami ssɛaren řejdud nneɣ Arebbi n ijenwan, aqa iwca i-ten deg ufus n Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, Axaldiwi, wenni ihedmen Taddart-a u indeh řgens ɣar lmenfa ɣar Babil. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt 2 Im. 36:16-21\x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 Maca deg useggʷas amezwaru n Kurac, ajeǧid n Babil, yumur Kurac ad ssbedden Taddart-a n Arebbi \add twařat nneɣni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt 2 Im. 36:22, 23; Ɛiz. 1\x*
\v 14 Uřa d řeqcuɛ n wureɣ d nnuqart zi Taddart n Arebbi, tinni ikkes Nabuxadnaṣṣar zi Zzawect Tameqqrant di Urcalim, issidef i-tent ɣar zzawect n Babil, aqa issuffeɣ i-tent Kurac zi zzawect di Babil u iwca \add i-tent\add* i \add ijj n weryaz\add* qqaren as Cicbaṣṣar, wenni tuɣa igga d lwali. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Ɛiz. 1:8\x*
\v 15 Netta inna as: Ksi řeqcuɛ-a, ruḥ, ggem ten di Zzawect Tameqqrant di Urcalim. Ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwabna Taddart n Arebbi deg wemcan nnes \add n zic\add*.
\m 
\v 16 Xas uca yusa-dd Cicbaṣṣar wanita, uca issars dsusa i Taddart n Arebbi di Urcalim u ssenni ař řexxu aqa bennan \add tt\add*, \add maca\add* war tᵉttwakemmeř \add ɛad\add*.’
\v 17 Xenni řexxu, mařa yarḍa i ujeǧid, ejj ad arzun deg wexxam n txubay n ujeǧid di Babil, ma s tidett immewc řumur zi ɣar ujeǧid Kurac ḥima ad tᵉttwabna Taddart-a n Arebbi di Urcalim twařa nneɣni uca ad aneɣ dd-ittwassekk \add xenni\add* lqarar n ujeǧid.”
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Řumur n ujeǧid Dariyus
\m 
\v 1 Xenni issuffeɣ ujeǧid Dariyus řumur uca arzun di taddart n idlisen ittwannḍen, mani ttwaxemmřent txubay din di Babil.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ittwaf di Aḥmata ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen di lqelɛa tenni \add iǧan\add* di lɛamala n Midya u dayes tuɣa tira-ya n řidaret:
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Deg useggʷas amezwaru n ujeǧid Kurac, issuffeɣ Kurac řumur-a: ‘\add X\add* Taddart n Arebbi di Urcalim. Aqa ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwabna Taddart nni \add twařa nneɣnit\add* deg wemcan mani qeddmen tiɣarṣa u \add ittxeṣṣa\add* ad ttwaɛeddřen dsusa nnes. Řuɛřa nnes \add ad tiři\add* settin n iɣaǧen, tiru nnes settin n iɣaǧen,
\v 4 s třata n řesdud n tṣuḍar timeqqranin d ijj n ssedd n tefřawt d jdid. Min din ixeṣṣen ad zzayes tᵉttwakellef zi taddart n ujeǧid.
\v 5 Uřa d řeqcuɛ n wureɣ d nnuqart n Taddart n Arebbi, tinni ikkes Nabuxadnaṣṣar zi Zzawect Tameqqrant nni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim u iwyi tent ɣar Babil, ad ttwarrent. man aya \add marra\add* ad dd-idweř ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant di Urcalim, ɣar wemcan nnes. Ittxeṣṣa ad temmarsed marra man aya di Taddart n Arebbi.’
\b
\m 
\v 6 S uya, Tatnay, lwali n \add temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, Catar-Buznay d iqqrinen nnes di řxedmet, iqqrinen nni \add iǧan\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, aggʷejem ssenni!
\v 7 Jjem řxedmet di ṭṭweɛ n Taddart-a n Arebbi, \add ḥima\add* lwali n Wudayen ak-d imɣaren n Wudayen ad bnan Taddart-a n Arebbi twařa nneɣnit deg wemcan nnes.
\v 8 Ɛawed ittwassuffeɣ-dd zzayi řumur x min ittxeṣṣa ad teggem i imɣaren n Wudayen-a maḥend ad tᵉttwabna Taddart-a n Arebbi \add twařat nneɣni\add*. Zeg wagřa n ujeǧid, zi ljizya \add n temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, ad ittwaxeǧeṣ s cḍaret min ittxeṣṣen iryazen-a maḥend war tᵉttbeddi ca \add řxedmet\add*.
\v 9 U min ittxeṣṣen zeg ifunasen imeẓyanen d icarriyyen d izmaren d tɣarṣi n wecmaḍ i Arebbi n ijenwan, u min ittxeṣṣen zeg irden d tmeǧaḥt d binu d zzect ɛlaḥsab awař n ikehhanen i iǧan di Urcalim, ad asen immewc zeg wass ɣar wass, ḥima war ittxeṣṣi uřa d walu,
\v 10 ḥima ad qeddmen ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i Arebbi n ijenwan uca ad ẓẓaǧen di ṭṭweɛ n tudart n ujeǧid d iḥenjiren nnes.
\m 
\v 11 ittwassuffeɣ-dd zzayi řumur ḥima kuř ijjen wenni i ɣa ibeddřen tawṣeyyet-a, ad ittwakkes ijj n weɛmud zi taddart nnes ad t ssbedden, ad xas ittwayeř netta uca di ssibbet-a ad tedweř taddart nnes d ict n tzubact n řeɣbar. \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt 2 Ij. 10:27; Dan. 2:5; 3:29. \x*
\m 
\v 12 Ejj ad ihdem Arebbi, wenni din issezdɣen Isem nnes, kuř ajeǧid d kuř řgens nni i ɣa isswiẓẓḍen afus nnes maḥend ad ibeddeř niɣ ad yareddeǧ Taddart n Arebbi nni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim. Necc Dariyus, d wenni iwcin řumur. Ejj ad ittwagg man aya s cḍaret.”
\b
\s1 Adeccen n Zzawect Tameqqrant d Řɛid amezwaru n Tɣarṣt n Useɛdu
\m 
\v 13 Xenni Tatnay, lwali \add n temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, ak-d Catar-Buznay d iqrinen nnes di řxedmet ggin s cḍaret ɛlaḥsab \add řumur\add* i tuɣa dd-issekk ujeǧid Dariyus.
\v 14 Bnan imɣaren n Wudayen u nitni arnin mliḥ \add di řebni\add* umi tuɣa ittnebba Ḥaggay d Zakariyya, mmis n Ɛiddu. Nitni bnan u kemmřen tt ɛlaḥsab řumur n Arebbi n Israil u ɛlaḥsab řumur n Kurac d Dariyus d Artaḥcasta, ajeǧid n Lfurs.
\v 15 Uca \add ammu\add* tᵉttwakemmeř Taddart deg wass wiss třata n uyur Adar, aqa-t d aseggʷas wiss setta n tgelda n ujeǧid Dariyus.
\v 16 Ayt n Israil, ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d ayt n lmenfa i iqqimen, deccnen Taddart-a n Arebbi s řefraḥet.
\v 17 I udeccen n Taddart n Arebbi iwyen nitni mya n ifunasen, mitayen n icarriyyen d arebɛa-mya n izmaren \add d taɣarṣt\add*, u i taɣarṣt n ddenb tenɛac n imuyan i marra Israil ɛlaḥsab řqedd n tqebbař n Israil.
\v 18 Nitni ssbedden ikehhanen s terbiɛin nsen u Ilawiyyen di terbiɛin nsen i tsexxart i Arebbi nni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim, ɛlaḥsab tawṣeyyet n wedlis n Musa. \x ◘ \xo 6:18 \xt Řxř. 3:6, 32; 8:11; 1 Im. 24:1\x*
\b
\m 
\v 19 Deg \add wass\add* wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur amezwaru sswejden ayt n lmenfa i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt Uf. 12:1-28; Lawi 23:5; Řxř. 28:16; Aɛwd. 16:2\x*
\v 20 Minzi ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen ggin ad ssizdgen ixef nsen am yijj n weryaz. Tuɣa-ten marra d imezdagen u nitni ɣarṣen \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i marra ayt n lmenfa u i aytmatsen ikehhanen u i yixef nsen.
\v 21 Ayt n Israil, inni dd-iɛeqben zi lmenfa, ccin zzayes, uřa d kuř ijjen wenni tuɣa issarxun ixef nnes zi řexmej n řegnus n temmurt \add uca\add* \add yusa-dd\add* ɣarsen ḥima ad yarzu SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 22 Sebɛa n wussan ɛeyyden nitni Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun, minzi SIDI tuɣa issefraḥ i-ten uca issmeyyeř uř n ujeǧid n Accur ɣarsen maḥend ad issejhed ifassen nsen ɣar řxedmet n Taddart n AREBBI, AREBBI n Israil.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Řumur n ujeǧid Artaḥcasta i Ɛizra
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya, řami tuɣa d tagelda n Artaḥcasta, ajeǧid n Lfurs, aqa \add din\add* Ɛizra, mmis n Saraya, mmis n Ɛazarya, mmis n Ḥilqiya,
\v 2 mmis n Callum, mmis n Ṣaduq, mmis n Axiṭub,
\v 3 mmis n Amarya, mmis n Ɛazarya, mmis n Marayut,
\v 4 mmis n Zaraḥ-Yah, mmis n Ɛuzi, mmis n Buqqi,
\v 5 mmis n Abicuɛa, mmis n Finḥas, mmis n Aliɛazar, mmis n Harun, arrays n ikehhanen.
\m 
\v 6 Ɛizra wanita igeɛɛed-dd zi Babil. Netta tuɣa d ijj n umseřmad d amiɣis n Ccariɛa n Musa tenni tuɣa i d iwca SIDI, Arebbi n Israil, uca ajeǧid iwca as marra x tutra nnes minzi afus n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, tuɣa-t xas.
\v 7 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa n ujeǧid Artaḥcasta geɛɛden akides ɣar Urcalim \add ijj n řqedd\add* n ayt n Israil d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d imedyazen d iɛessasen n tewwura d imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant. \f ◼ \fr 7:7 \fk imedyazen\ft - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen’.\f*
\v 8 Deg uyur wiss xemsa n useggʷas wiss sebɛa n ujeǧid yiweḍ Ɛizra ɣar Urcalim.
\v 9 Deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n uyur amezwaru \add tuɣa-t d\add* beddu n wuffuɣ zi Babil uca deg umezwaru n uyur wiss xemsa yiweḍ ɣar Urcalim, minzi tuɣa afus iṣebḥen n AREBBI xas,
\v 10 maɣar Ɛizra igga deg wuř nnes ad yarzu di Ccariɛa n SIDI u ad tt igg u ad isseřmed tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ di Israil.
\m 
\v 11 Ta d tiřemt n tebrat i iwca ujeǧid Artaḥcasta ak-d Ɛizra, akehhan d umseřmad n tira \add iqeddsen\add*, \add wenni d\add* amseřmad deg wawařen n řumurat n SIDI d tweṣṣa nnes i Israil:
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Artaḥcasta, ajeǧid n ijeǧiden, i Ɛizra, akehhan d umseřmad n Ccariɛa n Arebbi n ijenwan, řehna imun! ... uca ɛad.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Ittwassuffeɣ-dd zzayi řumur ḥima kuř ijj di tgeldit inu zi řgens n Israil u zeg ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, wenni s yixef nnes ixs ad yuyur ɣar Urcalim, ad kidek yuyur.
\v 14 Aqa cek tᵉttwassekked s ufus n ujeǧid d sebɛa n imcawaren nnes ḥima ad tbeqqced di mammec teǧa řḥař di Yahuda u di Urcalim, ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n Arebbi tenni \add iǧan\add* deg ifassen nnec.
\v 15 \add Tᵉttwasekked ɛawed\add* ḥima ad din tawyed nnuqart d wureɣ nni tuɣa iwca ujeǧid d imcawaren nnes s řxaḍar i Arebbi n Israil, wenni ɣar teǧa Tzeddiɣt di Urcalim, \x ◘ \xo 7:15 \xt Ɛiz. 8:25\x*
\v 16 u \add ɛawed\add* marra nnuqart d wureɣ i ɣa tafed di marra lɛamala n Babil, ak-d tewhibin n uṭewweɛ n řgens d ikehhanen, \add zeg\add* inni i ɣa iwcen s uṭewweɛ i Taddart n Arebbi nsen tenni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim,
\v 17 ḥima xenni ad tesɣed s nnuqart-a s cḍaret ifunasen, icarriyyen, izmaren ak-d tewhibin nnes \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibin n useyyeb ḥima ad tent tqeddmed x uɛalṭar n Taddart n Arebbi nnec, tenni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim.
\v 18 S min ɣa iqqimen n nnuqart d wureɣ ggem zzayes min tᵉttwařid cek d aytmac mliḥ, ɛlaḥsab řxaḍar n Arebbi nwem.
\v 19 Uca řeqcuɛ i d ac immewcen i tsexxart di Taddart n Arebbi, seɛdu ten \add ɣar din\add* zzat Arebbi n Urcalim.
\v 20 Min ɣa ixeṣṣen ɛad ktar i Taddart n Arebbi nnec, min ɣa yiři xak ad t txeǧṣed, ewc i-t zeg wexxam n txubay n ujeǧid.
\v 21 Necc, ajeǧid Artaḥcasta, ssuffeɣ-dd řumur i marra imeḥḍayen x txubay \add di temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, maḥend ad immewc s cḍaret marra min zzaywem ɣa ittar ukehhan Ɛizra, amseřmad n Ccariɛa n Arebbi n ijenwan,
\v 22 ař mya talint n nnuqart, ař mya ikuruten n irden, ař mya ibatuten n binu u ař mya ibatuten n zzect, uca \add i\add* tmeǧaḥt \add war din\add* bu tewṣeyyet.
\v 23 Marra min \add iǧan\add* zi řumur n Arebbi n ijenwan, ad ittwagg s cḍaret i Taddart n Arebbi n ijenwan, minzi mayemmi i dd ɣa yas weɣḍab x tgeldit n ujeǧid d iḥenjiren nnes?
\v 24 Zi jjihet n marra ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, d imeɣnujen d iɛessasen n tewwura d imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant d imsexxaren n Taddart n Arebbi wanita, aqa ad kenniw nxebbar, war izemmar ad xasen ittwagg řeɛcur, řa d ljizya uřa d ḍḍariba n webrid.
\v 25 Maca cek, Ɛizra, s tiɣit i d ac immewcen zi Arebbi nnec, řeqqem imḍebbaren d řquḍat nni i ɣa iḥekmen x marra řgens nni iǧan \add di temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, i marra inni issnen izerfan n Arebbi. Uca i yinni war ten issinen, ittxeṣṣa ad ten dd-tessargbed. \f ◼ \fr 7:25 \fk řeqqem\ft - niɣ ‘semma’.\f*
\v 26 Kuř ijjen wenni war iḍfaren Ccariɛa n Arebbi nwem d uzerf n ujeǧid, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaḥkem s cḍaret, ma s řmewt niɣ s lmenfa niɣ s multa n wagřa niɣ s řeḥbes.”
\b
\m 
\v 27 Asemɣar i SIDI, Arebbi n řejdud nneɣ, wenni iggin aya ammu deg wuř n ujeǧid ḥima ad yarni acenneɛ di Taddart n SIDI nni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim.
\v 28 Aqa Netta isscen ayi tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren zzat i wudem n ujeǧid d imcawaren nnes d marra řḥukkam ijehden n ujeǧid! Uca umi xafi tuɣa afus n SIDI, AREBBI inu, ggiɣ uř u ssmuneɣ izeǧifen n Israil ḥima ad kidi geɛɛden.
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Lista n yinni dd-idewřen ak-d Ɛizra
\m 
\v 1 Ina d izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add*, ak-d lista n jjadira nsen, inni akidi dd igeɛɛden zi Babil umi tuɣa teǧa tgelda n ujeǧid Artaḥcasta.
\b
\m 
\v 2 Zeg ayt n Finḥas: Jarcum,
\m zeg ayt n Itamar: Daniyal,
\m zeg ayt n Dawud: Ḥaṭṭuc.
\m 
\v 3 Zeg ayt n Cakanya, zeg ayt n Faruc: Zakariyya u akides ttwazemmemen mya u-xemsin n yeryazen ak-d jjadira nsen.
\m 
\v 4 Zeg ayt n Faḥat-Mu’ab: Ilyuɛinay, mmis n Zaraḥ-Yah, u akides mitayen n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 5 Zeg ayt n Cakanya, mmis n Yaḥziyil, u akides teřt-mya n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 6 Zeg ayt n Ɛadin: Ɛabid, mmis n Yunatan, u akides xemsin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 7 Zeg ayt n Ɛilam: Icaɛya, mmis n Ɛatalya, u akides sebɛin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 8 Zeg ayt n Cafaṭya: Zabadya, mmis n Mixayil, u akides tmenyin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 9 Zeg ayt n Yuwab: Ɛubadya, mmis n Yaḥiyil, u akides mitayen u-tmentac n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 10 Zeg ayt n Bani: Calumit, mmis n Yucafya, u akides mya u-settin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 11 Zeg ayt n Babay: Zakariyya, mmis n Babay, u akides tmenya u-ɛicrin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 12 Zeg ayt n Ɛajad: Yuḥanan, mmis n Haqqaṭan, u akides mya u-ɛecra n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 13 Zeg ayt n Aduniqam, ineggura, d ina d ismawen \add nsen\add*: Ilifalaṭ, Yaɛiyil d Camɛiya u akidsen settin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 14 Zeg ayt n Biɣway: Ɛutay d Zabbud u akides sebɛin n yeryazen.
\b
\s1 Asafar d twasit ɣar Urcalim
\m 
\v 15 Necc ssmuneɣ ten ɣar iɣzar nni ittekken x Ahawa. Dinni newta iqiḍan nneɣ třata n wussan u necc ḥekkareɣ i řgens d ikehhanen u war ufiɣ uřa d ijjen zeg Ilawiyyen.
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ssekkeɣ ɣar Aliɛazar, Ariyil, Camɛiya, Il-Natan, Yarib, Alnatan, Natan, Zakariyya u ɣar Macullam, \add inni d\add* izeǧifen, u ɣar Yuyarib d Il-Natan, \add iryazen\add* ɣarsen řefhamet.
\v 17 Umureɣ ten x Ɛiddu, azeǧif deg wemcan \add umi qqaren\add* Kasifya, uca ggiɣ asen awařen deg uqemmum nsen, ḥima ad ten inin i Ɛiddu, i učmas u i imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant deg wemcan \add umi qqaren\add* Kasifya, maḥend ad aneɣ dd-awyen imsexxaren i Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ.
\v 18 Umi tuɣa xaneɣ afus iṣebḥen n AREBBI, ssekken aneɣ-dd ijj n weryaz s řefhamet, ijjen zeg iḥenjiren n Maḥli, mmis n Lawi, mmis n Israil, u \add wanita\add* d Carabya, ak-d iḥenjiren nnes d aytmas, \add marra idsen\add* tmenṭac \add n yeryazen\add*,
\v 19 u \add ɛawed\add* Ḥacabya u akides Icaɛya zeg ayt n Marari, ak-d aytmas d iḥenjiren nsen, ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.
\v 20 U zeg imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant nni iwcin Dawud d řḥukkam i Ilawiyyen maḥend ad asen sexxaren, aqa aten mitayen u-ɛicrin n imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant inni marra ttwařaɣan s ismawen nsen.
\m 
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* řaɣiɣ dinni ɣar iɣzar n Ahawa s yijj n uẓummi, maḥend ad nessaḍar ixef nneɣ zzat i wudem n AREBBI nneɣ, maḥend ad zzayes nettar ticři d tamimunt i neccin u i tarwa nneɣ imeẓyanen u i wagřa nneɣ,
\v 22 maɣar ttsedḥiɣ ad ttareɣ ijj n řɛeskar zi ɣar ujeǧid maḥend ad aneɣ tɛawen deg webrid ḍidd i řeɛdu, minzi tuɣa nessawař deg ujeǧid, nenna: “Afus n AREBBI aqa-t d aṣebḥan x marra inni t yarezzun, maca jjehd nnes d weɣḍab nnes \add ad dd-asen\add* x marra inni i xas ittaggʷejen.”
\v 23 Iwa neccin nẓumm u nettar aya zi AREBBI nneɣ u netta istajeb aneɣ i tẓaǧit yuǧɣen nneɣ.
\m 
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* farzeɣ tenɛac \add n yeryazen\add* zeg imeqqranen n ikehhanen: Carabya d Ḥacabya u akidsen ɛecra n aytmatsen.
\v 25 Wezneɣ zzatsen nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ, aqa aya d tawhibt n usgeɛɛed i Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ, tenni issgeɛɛed ujeǧid ak-d imcawaren nnes d řḥukkam nnes d marra inni \add din\add* ittwafen zi Israil. \x ◘ \xo 8:25 \xt Ɛiz. 7:14, 15\x*
\v 26 Wezneɣ u ggiɣ asen deg ifassen nsen setta-mya u-xemsin talint n nnuqart u mya n řeqcuɛ n nnuqart \add iweznen\add* mya talint u mya talint n wureɣ
\v 27 u ɛicrin n ifenjařen n wureɣ sekkʷan ařef draxmat uřa d tnayen n řeqcuɛ n nnḥas, icellel, icna, iɣřa am wureɣ.
\v 28 Nniɣ asen: “Kenniw d imqeddasen zzat i SIDI u řeqcuɛ-a aqa qeddsen \add i ǧan\add*, uřa d nnuqart-a d wureɣ-a, aqa aya d tawhibt s řxaḍar i SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem.
\v 29 Ɛessem u ḥḍam aya ař t ɣa tweznem zzat i wudem n imeqqranen n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d imeqqranen n \add řaǧat n\add* ibabaten n Israil di Urcalim, deg ixxamen n Taddart n SIDI.”
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ṭṭfen ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen řewzen n nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ ḥima ad awyen \add aya marra\add* ɣar Urcalim ɣar Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ.
\m 
\v 31 Deg wass wiss tenɛac n uyur amezwaru nekkes iqiḍan nneɣ maḥend ad nuyur ɣar Urcalim. Tuɣa afus n AREBBI xaneɣ uca ifekk aneɣ zeg ufus n řeɛdu u \add zeg ufus\add* n yinni \add i d aneɣ\add* iggin řfex deg webrid.
\v 32 Uca niweḍ ɣar Urcalim u neqqim dinni třata n wussan.
\v 33 Deg wass wiss arebɛa ittwawzen nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ di Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ uca newca aya i ukehhan Marimut, mmis n Uriya, uca Aliɛazar, mmis n Finḥas, \add tuɣa-t\add* akides uřa d Yuzabad, mmis n Yecuɛa, d Nuɛadya, mmis n Bannuy, nitni s tnayen d Ilawiyyen.
\v 34 \add D man aya imsar\add* ɛlaḥsab řqedd d řewzen n marra aya u marra řewzen ittwawzen di řweqt nni d ijjen.
\v 35 Ayt n lmenfa inni dd-iɛeqben zi tmeḥbast, ssgeɛɛden i AREBBI n Israil tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ: tenɛac n ifunasen imeẓyanen i marra Israil, setta u-tesɛin n icarriyyen u sebɛa u-sebɛin n izmaren, u i tɣarṣt n ddenb tenɛac n imuyan, marra aya d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.
\v 36 Nitni wcin tiweṣṣa n ujeǧid i ijeǧiden \add i iǧan\add* sadu ujeǧid u i lwulat \add di temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* u nitni wcin afus i řgens u \add i tsexxart di\add* Taddart n AREBBI.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Tẓaǧit d ndamet n Ɛizra
\m 
\v 1 Awarni řami ittwakemmeř man aya \add marra\add*, usin-dd ɣari řḥukkam, nnan: “Řgens n Israil d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen war qqimen ttwamsebḍan x řegnus n temmura-ya, \add maɣar\add* jjɛayef nsen am tinni n ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Ifiriziyyen d Iyabusiyyen d ayt n Ɛammun d ayt n Mu’ab d Imiṣriyyen d Imuriyyen.
\v 2 Nitni iwyen zeg yessitsen \add timɣarin\add* i yixef nsen u i iḥenjiren nsen ařami ṣuren zzariɛet d tamqeddast s řegnus n temmura-ya, wah, afus n řḥukkam d imḍebbaren tuɣa-t d amezwaru di řeɣdar-a.”
\m 
\v 3 Umi sřiɣ aya, carrgeɣ arruḍ inu d useřham inu, qeřɛeɣ-dd acuwwaf n uzeǧif u n tmart uca qqimeɣ jeɛɛareɣ.
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* munen-dd xafi marra, inni ittarjijen zi AREBBI n Israil, di ssibbet n řeɣdar n ayt n lmenfa, maca necc qqimeɣ jeɛɛareɣ ař \add řweqt n\add* tewhibt n tmeddit. \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt Řxř. 28:1-8\x*
\v 5 Ɣar tewhibt n tmeddit kkareɣ zeg uswaḍeɛ inu s warruḍ inu d useřham inu \add icarrgen\add* uca uḍareɣ x ifadden u sswiẓẓḍeɣ ifassen inu ɣar SIDI, AREBBI inu. \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Řxř. 28:1-8\x*
\m 
\v 6 Nniɣ: “AREBBI inu, necc sedḥiɣ u ttwassbehdřeɣ ař war zɛimeɣ ad ɣarek dd-ssgeɛɛdeɣ udem inu, a AREBBI inu, minzi řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ temɣar aneɣ x uzeǧif u amarwas nneɣ imɣar ař ajenna. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Izhd. 38:5\x*
\v 7 Zeg wussan n řejdud nneɣ ař ass-a \add aqa aneɣ\add* deg umarwas d ameqqran u x řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ nemmewc neccin d ijeǧiden nneɣ d ikehhanen nneɣ deg ifassen n ijeǧiden n temmura, \add aqa nemmewc\add* i ssif, i tmeḥbast, i ukecceḍ u i řefḍiḥet x wudmawen nneɣ, am mammec \add i teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 8 Řexxu tuɣa din ict n tzeḥziḥt d tameẓyant n arḍa n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ḥima ad aneɣ yejj ca n yinni innejmen u ḥima ad aneɣ iwc ijj n řewted di Zzawect Tameqqrant nnes Iqeddsen u tfawt i tiṭṭawin nneɣ, \add a\add* AREBBI nneɣ, u ḥima ad aneɣ dd-yarr nnefs cwayt di tesmuɣi nneɣ.
\v 9 Aqa neccin d isemɣan, maca di tesmuɣi nneɣ war dayneɣ ismiḥ AREBBI nneɣ, maca Netta idřa aneɣ s tmexsiwt nnes icewwaren zzat i wudem n ijeǧiden n Lfurs maḥend ad aneɣ dd-yarr nnefs i usbeddi n Taddart n AREBBI \add twařat nneɣni\add*, i weɛdař n řxirbat u ḥima ad aneɣ iwc ijj n wemcan ittwannḍen s řḥiḍ di Yahuda u di Urcalim.”
\m 
\v 10 “Uca řexxu, min ɣa nini awarni uya ɛad, \add a\add* AREBBI nneɣ, minzi nesmeḥ di řumurat nnec,
\v 11 tinni tumured s tsexxart n imsexxaren nnec, inabiyyen, inni innan: ‘Tammurt tenni i ɣa tadfem maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart, d ict n temmurt tᵉttwassexmej s řexmej n řegnus n temmura, s jjɛayef nsen i zi tt ccuren zi ṭṭarf ař ṭṭarf nneɣni s texmuji nsen’, \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Lawi 18:25, 27; Aɛwd. 7:3\x*
\m 
\v 12 \add d inni iqqaren uřa ɛad\add* řexxu: ‘War tticem tiḥenjirin nwem d timɣarin i iḥenjiren nsen, uřa d tiḥenjirin nsen war tent ttiwyem i iḥenjiren nwem uca war arezzum x řaman nsen niɣ řxar nsen i řebda, ḥima ad tdewřem tjehdem u ad teccem mummu \add n řɣiǧet\add* n temmurt u ad tt tewcem d řwart i řebda i iḥenjiren nwem.’”\x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Aɛwd. 7:3; 11:8; 23:7\x*
\m 
\v 13 “Uca awarni marra min i d aneɣ imsaren di ssibbet n tmegga nneɣ tiɛeffanin d umarwas nneɣ ameqqran, \add a\add* AREBBI nneɣ, aqa Cek war d aneɣ txeǧṣed ca mɣir drus waha ařami war nettwahellek ca s řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ u tewcid aneɣ \add ɛad\add* ina inni innejmen am tt teǧa \add řexxu\add*.
\v 14 Ma nzemmar řexxu ad narẓ twařa nneɣnit tiweṣṣa nnec u ad negg ad nedweř d iḍeggʷařen ak-d řegnus nni \add iggin\add* jjɛayef-a? Ma \add xenni\add* Cek war xaneɣ tseɛɛared ařami xaneɣ i ɣa teqḍid ař mani war ittɣimi ijj n řbaqi uřa d wenni innejmen?
\v 15 \add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, Cek d amsegged, minzi neccin d inni iqqimen nnejmen am \add teǧa\add* ass-a. Aqa neccin s umarwas \add i neǧa\add* zzat i wudem nnec, minzi uřa d ijjen war izemmar ad ibedd zzat i wudem nnec di ssibbet-a.”
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Řgens iggʷej x temɣarin iɣriben
\m 
\v 1 Umi iẓẓuǧ Ɛizra ammu, inɛem, iru uca iwḍa \add x ifadden\add* zzat i Taddart n AREBBI, aqa issmun-dd xas řɣaci d ameqqran aṭṭas n yeryazen d temɣarin d iḥenjiren n Israil, minzi řgens iru s imeṭṭawen imeqqranen.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* Cakanya, mmis n Yaḥiyil, ijjen zeg ayt n Ɛilam, iṭṭef deg wawař, inna i Ɛizra:
\b
\m “Neccin aqa neɣdar AREBBI nneɣ uca neccin niwi timɣarin tibarraniyyin zi řegnus n temmurt, nessezdeɣ i-tent akidneɣ. Xenni řexxu, aqa din \add ɛad\add* řayas i Israil di man aya.
\v 3 Ejj aneɣ ad negg ijj n řɛahd ak-d AREBBI ḥima ad naẓẓeř x marra timɣarin d min zzaysent dd-ixeřqen, ɛlaḥsab acawar n Sidi inu u n yinni ittarjijen i řumur n AREBBI, uca \add xenni\add* ad ittwagg ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa.
\v 4 Kkar, minzi tamesřact\add -a\add* aqa-tt x \add weɛrur\add* nnec u neccin akidek nbedd. Iři d aryaz, egg \add i-tt\add*!”
\b
\m 
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Ɛizra uca ijja imeqqranen n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d marra Israil ad jjaǧen ad ggen ɛlaḥsab awař-a uca nitni jjuǧen.
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Ɛizra \add iffeɣ\add* \add zi\add* zzat i wudem n Taddart n AREBBI, yudef ɣar wexxam n Yuḥanan, mmis n Ilyasib. \add Umi\add* yudef \add dinni\add*, war icci aɣrum war iswi aman, maɣar icḍen x řeɣdar n ayt n lmenfa.
\v 7 Uca ggin ijj n ubarreḥ di Yahuda d Urcalim i marra ayt n lmenfa maḥend ad munen di Urcalim.
\v 8 Qaɛ wenni war dd-yusin di \add řmijar n\add* třata n wussan, am mammec \add iǧa\add* deg ucawar n řḥukkam d iwessura, marra agřa nnes ad as ittwaḥarrem u netta simant nnes ad ittwammsebḍa x wegraw \add n řgens\add* n ayt n lmenfa
\m 
\v 9 Di třata n wussan nnjarwen marra iryazen n Yahuda d Binyamin di Urcalim. Tuɣa deg wass wiss ɛicrin n uyur wiss tesɛa. Marra řgens iqqim deg wazzay n Taddart n AREBBI, ttarjijen zi tmesřact\add -a\add* uřa zeg wenẓar i dd-iwettan s waṭṭas.
\v 10 Ikkar ukehhan Ɛizra, inna asen: “Kenniw teɣdarem u tiwyem timɣarin tibarraniyyin \add zi řegnus\add* tesszedɣem tent akidwem \add u ammu i\add* teggim tarnim deg umarwas n Israil.
\v 11 Xenni řexxu, qadam SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, u ggem min ixs Netta uca mmsebḍam x řegnus n temmurt uřa x temɣarin tibarraniyyin.”
\m 
\v 12 Marra agraw \add n řgens\add* yarra-dd xas s jjhed: “Aqa-t x \add weɛrur\add* nneɣ maḥend ad negg ɛlaḥsab awařen nnec!
\v 13 Maca aqa \add din\add* aṭṭas n iwdan u aqa d řweqt n wenẓar. War ɣarsen bu jjehd maḥend ad \add qqimen\add* bedden barra uřa d man aya war iǧi d ict n řxedmet n ijj niɣ tnayen n wussan, minzi aṭṭas zzayneɣ ɛeddan di tmesřact-a.
\v 14 Ejj ad bedden řḥukkam nneɣ di ṭṭweɛ n marra agraw \add n řgens\add* uca ad dd-asen deg wussan ittwaggen marra inni di tneddam yiwyen ɣarsen timɣarin tibarraniyyin, sszedɣen tent di tudrin nsen, uca \add jmiɛ akidsen\add* uřa d iwessura n kuř tandint d řquḍat nnes, ař xaneɣ ɣa ibeɛɛed řḥaduq n weɣḍab n AREBBI nneɣ.”
\m 
\v 15 Mɣir Yunatan, mmis Ɛasa’il, d Yaḥazya, mmis n Tiqwa, tuɣa ttɛekksen x man aya u Macullam d Cabatay, Alawi, wcin asen afus.
\m 
\v 16 \add Maca\add* iryazen nni iɛeqben zi lmenfa ggin \add t\add* ammu. \add Xenni\add* ittwafarz ukehhan Ɛizra \add d\add* yeryazen \add inni\add* d izeǧifen x ibabaten n řaǧat n ibabaten nsen. Nitni marra ttwařaɣan s yisem nsen uca qqimen deg wass amezwaru n uyur wiss ɛecra, ḥima ad arzun di tmesřact\add -a\add*.
\v 17 Deg wass amezwaru n uyur amezwaru kemmřen nitni \add tarezzut\add* di marra iryazen nni iggin ad sszedɣen akidsen timɣarin tibarraniyyin.
\v 18 Ittwaf belli inni zeg ayt n ikehhanen inni isszedɣen ɣar ixef nsen temɣarin tibarraniyyin, aqa aten zeg ayt n Yahucaɛ, mmis n Yuṣadaq, u zeg aytmas, Maɛasiya d Aliɛazar d Yarib d Jadalya.
\v 19 Nitni wtin x ufus ad ssekken timɣarin nsen, u umi daysen amarwas, \add ad awyen\add* ijjen zeg wuǧi i umarwas nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Zeg iḥenjiren n Immir: Ḥanani d Zabadya.
\m 
\v 21 Zeg iḥenjiren n Ḥarim: Maɛasiya, Iliya, Camɛiya, Yaḥiyil d Ɛuzziya.
\m 
\v 22 Zeg iḥenjiren n Facḥur: Ilyuɛinay, Maɛasiya, Ismaɛil, Natanayil, Yuzabad d Alɛasa.
\m 
\v 23 Zi Ilawiyyen: Juzabad, Cimɛi, Qalaya, \add wa d Qaliṭa\add*, d Fatḥya, Yahuda d Aliɛazar.
\m 
\v 24 Zeg imedyazen: Alyasib.
\m Zeg iɛessasen n tewwura: Callum, Ṭalam d Uri. \f ◼ \fr 10:24 \fk imedyazen\ft - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen’.\f*
\m 
\v 25 Zi Israil: zeg ayt n Farɛuc: Ramya, Jiziya, Malkiya, Miyamin, Aliɛazar, Malkiya d Banaya.
\m 
\v 26 Zeg ayt n Ɛilam: Mattanya, Zakariyya, Yaḥiyil, Ɛabdi, Yarimut d Iliya.
\m 
\v 27 Zeg ayt n Zattu: Ilyuɛinay, Ilyacib, Mattanya, Yarimut, Zabad d Ɛaziza.
\m 
\v 28 Zeg ayt n Babay: Yuḥanan, Ḥananya, Zabbay d Ɛatlay.
\m 
\v 29 Zeg ayt n Bani: Macullam, Mallux, Ɛadaya, Yacub, Ca’al d Yaramut.
\m 
\v 30 Zeg ayt n Faḥat-Mu’ab: Ɛadna, Kalal, Banaya, Maɛasiya, Mattanya, Baṣaliyil, Binnuy d Manassa.
\m 
\v 31 Zeg ayt n Ḥarim: Aliɛazar, Yacci-Yah, Malkiya, Camɛiya, Cimɛun,
\v 32 Binyamin, Mallux d Camarya.
\m 
\v 33 Zeg ayt n Ḥacum: Mattanay, Mattatta, Zabad, Ilifalaṭ, Yarimay, Manassa, Cimɛi.
\m 
\v 34 Zeg ayt n Bani: Maɛaday, Ɛamram d Uwyil,
\v 35 Banaya, Badya, Kaluhi,
\v 36 Wanya, Marimut, Ilyacib,
\v 37 Mattanya, Mattnay, Yaɛsu,
\v 38 Bani, Binnuy, Cimɛi,
\v 39 Calmaya, Natan, Ɛadaya,
\v 40 Maknadbay, Cacay, Caray,
\v 41 Ɛazaryil, Calamya, Camarya,
\v 42 Callum, Amarya, Yusuf.
\m 
\v 43 Zeg ayt n Nabu: Yaɛiyil, Mattitya, Zabad, Zabina, Yaddu, Yuwil d Banaya.
\b
\m 
\v 44 Marra ina tuɣa iwyen timɣarin tibarraniyyin uca ca zzaysen tuɣa ɣarsen timɣarin urwent-i-dd iḥenjiren. * 
